  <id>ATTR_CONTAINED_L3_CONFIG</id>
  <targetType>TARGET_TYPE_PROC_CHIP</targetType>
  <description>
    During a contained IPL the instance-specific L3 configuration needs to be
    saved and restored since all L3 instances are scanned using identical
    inits. This attribute holds these configuration settings.
    Array structure: ATTR_CONTAINED_L3_CONFIG[core][reg], where there are 32
